{"type":"text","timestamp":1777038244713,"sessionID":"ses_24044f74bffeTPRnDDunHW1Zuc","part":{"id":"prt_dbfbbad24001ntq18SvT2h9nc5","messageID":"msg_dbfbba418001FaABTVnwcoJz9h","sessionID":"ses_24044f74bffeTPRnDDunHW1Zuc","type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've created a fully playable Snake game in a single self-contained HTML file called `index.html`. Here's what's included:\n\n**Features:**\n- Arrow key controls (up, down, left, right)\n- Score tracking with high score persistence (stored in localStorage)\n- Game over detection (wall collision and self-collision)\n- Restart functionality via button or after game over\n- Polished visual design with:\n  - Gradient background\n  - Glassmorphic game container\n  - Gradient snake with shine effect on head\n  - Glowing food with sparkle effect\n  - Subtle grid lines\n  - Smooth animations\n  - Game over modal overlay\n\n**How to play:**\n1. Open `index.html` in any web browser\n2. Press any arrow key to start the game\n3. Use arrow keys to control the snake\n4. Eat the red food to grow and score points\n5. Avoid hitting walls or yourself\n6. Click \"Restart Game\" or \"Play Again\" to restart\n\nThe game includes proper collision detection, prevents moving backwards into yourself, and has a modern, polished UI with smooth animations. Your high score is automatically saved between sessions!","time":{"start":1777038241060,"end":1777038244712}}}
